in Slovenia (
Gogala & Trilar, 2004
), Switzerland (
Hertach, 2004
), Austria (
Trilar & Holzinger, 2004
), Germany (A. Staudt in
Trilar & Holzinger, 2004
), Macedonia (
Gogala, et al., 2005
), Montenegro and Poland (
Trilar, et al., 2006
), can now be attributed to
C. cantilatrix
sp. nov.
